Topic_NPS_Scores_ove_1.query:
q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponsewithDetails_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";
q = filter q by 'Question_QuestionType' == "NPS";
promoters = filter q by 'NumberValue' > 8;
detractors = filter q by 'NumberValue' < 7;
Score_by_topic = group q by ('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name') left,  promoters by ('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name') left, detractors by ('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name');
Score_by_topic = foreach Score_by_topic generate q.'CreatedDate_Year' + "~~~" + q.'CreatedDate_Month' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month', q.'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' as 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name', round(((count(promoters) - count(detractors))*100)/count(q),2) as 'NPS';
Score_by_topic = order Score_by_topic by ('CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month' asc, 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' asc);

Trend_of_ratings_ass_1.query:
